  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<em>Foes that you drag are thrown out of balance.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Str 13, Improved Drag, Power Attack, base attack bonus +6.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>You receive a +2 bonus on checks made to drag a foe. This bonus stacks with the bonus granted by Improved Drag. Whenever you drag a foe, his movement provokes attacks of opportunity from all of your allies (but not you).<br/><br/><b>Normal</b><br/>Creatures moved by drag do not provoke attacks of opportunity.<br/><br/><b>Combat Trick</b><br/>When you succeed at a drag combat maneuver check, you can spend 5 stamina points to gain up to 10 feet of movement for your drag. You can use this movement in place of your normal movement, but only to drag an opponent.",
